<h2>List Item Type</h2>
<h3>Dynamic</h3>
<p>Any of
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @onClick " />
  ,
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @route " />
  or
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @href " />
  param has to be added to
  <Hds::Badge @text="&lt;Cut::ListItem /&gt;" />
  to make it dynamic type. For interactive elements with
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @route " />
  or
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @href " />
  , list item work similar as
  <Hds::Badge @text="Hds::Interactive" />
  element. Actually
  <Hds::Badge @text="Cut::ListItem" />
  uses the hds component as a wrapper for content and actions for the case.
</p>
<pre><code>
    &lt;Cut::ListItem @route='dummy' as |L|&gt; &lt;L.Content>Service
    a&lt;/L.Content&gt; &lt;/Cut::ListItem&gt; &lt;Cut::ListItem @href="#"
    @isHrefExternal={{false}}
    as |L|&gt; &lt;L.Content>Service b&lt;/L.Content&gt; &lt;/Cut::ListItem&gt;
  </code></pre>
<div class="doc-list-container">
  <Cut::ListItem @route="dummy" as |L|>
    <L.Content>Element with route added</L.Content>
  </Cut::ListItem>
  <Cut::ListItem @href="#" @isHrefExternal={{false}} as |L|>
    <L.Content>Element with href and isHrefExternal set to false</L.Content>
    <L.ActionDropdown as |dd|>
      <dd.ToggleIcon
        @icon="more-horizontal"
        @text="Menu"
        @hasChevron={{false}}
      />
      <dd.Interactive @icon="edit" @text="Edit" />
    </L.ActionDropdown>
  </Cut::ListItem>
  <Cut::ListItem @onClick={{this.onItemClicked}} as |L|>
    <L.Content>Element with onClick</L.Content>
    <L.ActionDropdown as |dd|>
      <dd.ToggleIcon
        @icon="more-horizontal"
        @text="Menu"
        @hasChevron={{false}}
      />
      <dd.Interactive @icon="edit" @text="Edit" />
    </L.ActionDropdown>
  </Cut::ListItem>
</div>
<h3>Static</h3>
<p>Static type is default for
  <Hds::Badge @text="Cut::ListItem" />
  , if none of the
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @onClick " />
  ,
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @route " />
  or
  <Hds::Badge @text=" @href " />
  params is passed.
</p>
<pre><code>
    &lt;Cut::ListItem as |L|&gt; &lt;L.Content>Service a&lt;/L.Content&gt;
    &lt;/Cut::ListItem&gt;
  </code></pre>
<div class="doc-list-container">
  <Cut::ListItem as |L|>
    <L.Content><div {{hds-tooltip "hello"}}>Service a</div></L.Content>
  </Cut::ListItem>
  <Cut::ListItem as |L|>
    <L.Content><Cut::CopyBlock @clipboardText="Service b">Service b</Cut::CopyBlock></L.Content>
    <L.ActionDropdown as |dd|>
      <dd.ToggleIcon
